---
import Main from '../layouts/main.astro';

const FRAUNCES_URL =
  'https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fraunces:ital,opsz,wght@0,9..144,300;0,9..144,400;0,9..144,600;1,9..144,400&display=swap';

const sectionClass = 'py-8 border-t border-slate-700';
const summarySectionClass = 'pt-8 pb-8';
const containerClass = 'max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6';
const slotCards = [
  { time: '10:05 – 10:55', label: 'Full hour' },
  { time: '10:05 – 10:30', label: 'First half of the hour' },
  { time: '10:35 – 11:00', label: 'Second half of the hour' },
];
---

<Main
  title="Start at :05 — Smarter meeting times | Gerrit Garbereder"
  description="Start meetings five minutes after the hour. Fewer late arrivals, calmer transitions, built-in breaks. A simple meeting policy that works."
  canonical="https://www.garbereder.com/start-at-05/"
  keywords="meeting policy, meeting times, Start at :05, scheduling, productivity, calendar, back-to-back meetings"
  extraFontUrl={FRAUNCES_URL}
>
  <div class="start-at-05 min-h-screen flex flex-col">
    <a
      href="#main-content"
      class="absolute left-[-9999px] top-4 z-[100] px-4 py-2 bg-slate-800 text-slate-100 rounded outline-2 outline-orange-400 outline-offset-2 focus:left-4 focus:outline"
    >
      Skip to main content
    </a>
    <header
      role="banner"
      class="relative overflow-hidden px-4 py-8 shadow-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-900 via-slate-800 to-slate-900 sm:py-12"
    >
      <div
        class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-3/4 h-full max-w-xl bg-gradient-to-l from-orange-500/15 to-transparent pointer-events-none"
        aria-hidden="true"
      >
      </div>
      <div class={`${containerClass} relative z-10`}>
        <h1
          class="start-at-05-h1 text-slate-300 font-light leading-tight tracking-tight"
        >
          Start at <span class="text-orange-400 font-normal italic">:05</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="lead text-lg mt-8 max-w-[28ch] text-slate-400">
          Start meetings five minutes after the hour. Fewer late arrivals,
          calmer transitions, built-in breaks.
        </p>

        <!-- Timeline: vertical on small screens, horizontal on sm+ -->
        <div
          class="mt-8 py-8"
          role="img"
          aria-label="Timeline: 10:00, 10:05 start, 10:55 end, 11:00"
        >
          <!-- Vertical timeline (mobile) -->
          <ul
            class="timeline-vertical sm:hidden border-l-2 border-slate-500 space-y-8 list-none pl-0"
          >
            <li class="relative flex items-center min-h-[2rem] pl-8">
              <span
                class="timeline-dot absolute w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-slate-400"
                aria-hidden="true"></span>
              <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-400">10:00</span>
            </li>
            <li class="relative flex items-center min-h-[2rem] pl-8">
              <span
                class="timeline-dot absolute w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-orange-400 ring-4 ring-orange-400/30"
                aria-hidden="true"></span>
              <span class="timeline-label text-sm font-medium text-slate-300"
                >10:05 Start</span
              >
            </li>
            <li class="relative flex items-center min-h-[2rem] pl-8">
              <span
                class="timeline-dot absolute w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-orange-300 ring-4 ring-orange-300/30"
                aria-hidden="true"></span>
              <span class="timeline-label text-sm font-medium text-slate-300"
                >10:55 End</span
              >
            </li>
            <li class="relative flex items-center min-h-[2rem] pl-8">
              <span
                class="timeline-dot absolute w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-slate-400"
                aria-hidden="true"></span>
              <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-400">11:00</span>
            </li>
          </ul>

          <!-- Horizontal timeline (sm+) -->
          <div
            class="timeline-horizontal hidden sm:flex items-start justify-center gap-0 flex-nowrap"
          >
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-4 shrink-0">
              <span
                class="w-3.5 h-3.5 rounded-full bg-slate-400"
                aria-hidden="true"></span>
              <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-400">10:00</span>
            </div>
            <div
              class="timeline-connector mt-2 w-6 sm:w-8 h-0.5 rounded bg-slate-500 shrink-0 max-w-[40px]"
              aria-hidden="true"
            >
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-4 shrink-0">
              <span
                class="w-3.5 h-3.5 rounded-full bg-orange-400 ring-4 ring-orange-400/30"
                aria-hidden="true"></span>
              <span class="timeline-label text-sm font-medium text-slate-300"
                >10:05 Start</span
              >
            </div>
            <div
              class="timeline-connector mt-2 flex-1 min-w-[24px] h-0.5 rounded bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-400 to-orange-300"
              aria-hidden="true"
            >
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-4 shrink-0">
              <span
                class="w-3.5 h-3.5 rounded-full bg-orange-300 ring-4 ring-orange-300/30"
                aria-hidden="true"></span>
              <span class="timeline-label text-sm font-medium text-slate-300"
                >10:55 End</span
              >
            </div>
            <div
              class="timeline-connector mt-2 w-6 sm:w-8 h-0.5 rounded bg-slate-500 shrink-0 max-w-[40px]"
              aria-hidden="true"
            >
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-4 shrink-0">
              <span
                class="w-3.5 h-3.5 rounded-full bg-slate-400"
                aria-hidden="true"></span>
              <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-400">11:00</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </header>

    <main id="main-content" class="flex-1 bg-slate-900 text-slate-400">
      <article aria-label="Start at :05 meeting policy">
        <section class={sectionClass}>
          <div class={containerClass}>
            <h2
              class="start-at-05-h2 text-slate-100 mb-8 text-[1.875rem] font-light leading-snug"
            >
              Why not "on the hour"?
            </h2>
            <p class="lead text-lg mb-8">
              Meetings usually are about <strong class="text-slate-400"
                >30</strong
              > or <strong class="text-slate-400">60 minutes</strong> long. Many teams
              use 50‑minute slots to create buffers—but that creates friction too.
            </p>
            <div
              class="card my-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-600 bg-slate-800 p-6 text-base shadow-md"
            >
              <h3
                class="start-at-05-h3 text-orange-400 font-semibold uppercase text-[0.8125rem] tracking-widest leading-snug mb-8"
              >
                Problems with 50‑minute blocks
              </h3>
              <ul class="list m-0 flex list-none flex-col gap-4 p-0 text-base">
                <li
                  class="start-at-05-list-li flex gap-4 text-slate-400 leading-[1.5]"
                >
                  Rooms are often booked until the full hour anyway, so you
                  can't get in early.
                </li>
                <li
                  class="start-at-05-list-li flex gap-4 text-slate-400 leading-[1.5]"
                >
                  People think in round hours. "Meeting at 10:00" means they may
                  show at 10:00—and miss a 10:00 sharp start.
                </li>
                <li
                  class="start-at-05-list-li flex gap-4 text-slate-400 leading-[1.5]"
                >
                  It's easier to stick to the full 50 minutes by starting late
                  rather than by forcing a hard stop on the hour.
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class={sectionClass}>
          <div class={containerClass}>
            <h2
              class="start-at-05-h2 text-slate-100 mb-8 text-[1.875rem] font-light leading-snug"
            >
              The fix: Start at :05
            </h2>
            <p class="text-base mb-8">
              Schedule meetings to <span class="text-orange-400 font-semibold"
                >start at :05</span
              > (five minutes after the hour)—or at :35 for half-hour slots. You keep
              buffer time between back-to-backs while matching how people think about
              times: "meeting at 10" still gives a few minutes to get there, and you're
              done before the next round hour so the next meeting can start at :05
              too.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="band">
            <div class="band-inner mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6">
              <div
                class="card highlight my-0 rounded-2xl relative overflow-hidden border border-slate-600 bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-900 to-slate-800 p-6"
              >
                <h3
                  class="start-at-05-h3 text-orange-400 font-semibold uppercase text-[0.8125rem] tracking-widest leading-snug mb-8"
                >
                  Why it works
                </h3>
                <ul
                  class="list m-0 flex list-none flex-col gap-4 p-0 text-base"
                >
                  <li
                    class="start-at-05-list-li flex gap-4 text-slate-400 leading-[1.5]"
                  >
                    People still think "on the hour" but you start at :05 (or
                    :35).
                  </li>
                  <li
                    class="start-at-05-list-li flex gap-4 text-slate-400 leading-[1.5]"
                  >
                    Everyone gets at least a 5‑minute break between meetings.
                  </li>
                  <li
                    class="start-at-05-list-li flex gap-4 text-slate-400 leading-[1.5]"
                  >
                    "Meeting at 10" still gives a 5‑minute window to reach the
                    room.
                  </li>
                  <li
                    class="start-at-05-list-li flex gap-4 text-slate-400 leading-[1.5]"
                  >
                    Encouraged to end on time by following meetings.
                  </li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class={`${containerClass} pt-8`}>
            <h3
              class="start-at-05-h3 text-orange-400 font-semibold uppercase text-[0.8125rem] tracking-widest leading-snug mb-4"
            >
              Examples
            </h3>
            <p class="text-base mb-4">
              For <strong class="text-slate-400">60‑minute</strong> meetings, start
              at :05 and end at :55.
            </p>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 mb-8">
              <div
                class="slot rounded-xl border border-slate-600 bg-slate-800 p-6 text-center text-base shadow-md"
              >
                <div class="time text-orange-400 font-light text-2xl mb-4">
                  {slotCards[0].time}
                </div>
                <div class="label text-sm text-slate-400">
                  {slotCards[0].label}
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <p class="text-base mb-4">
              For <strong class="text-slate-400">30‑minute</strong> meetings, start
              at :05 or :35.
            </p>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 sm:grid-cols-2">
              {
                slotCards.slice(1).map((slot) => (
                  <div class="slot rounded-xl border border-slate-600 bg-slate-800 p-6 text-center text-base shadow-md">
                    <div class="time text-orange-400 font-light text-2xl mb-4">
                      {slot.time}
                    </div>
                    <div class="label text-sm text-slate-400">{slot.label}</div>
                  </div>
                ))
              }
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class={summarySectionClass}>
          <div class="band">
            <div class="band-inner mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6">
              <div
                class="card highlight my-0 rounded-2xl relative overflow-hidden border border-slate-600 bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-900 to-slate-800 p-6"
              >
                <h2
                  class="start-at-05-h2 text-orange-400 font-light text-[1.875rem] leading-snug mb-8"
                >
                  Summary
                </h2>
                <p class="text-base mb-8">
                  By consistently using <span
                    class="font-semibold text-orange-400">Start at :05</span
                  > (and :35 for half-hour slots), we:
                </p>
                <ul
                  class="list m-0 flex list-none flex-col gap-4 p-0 text-base"
                >
                  <li
                    class="start-at-05-list-li flex gap-4 text-slate-400 leading-[1.5]"
                  >
                    Reduce lateness from "on-the-hour" mental scheduling
                  </li>
                  <li
                    class="start-at-05-list-li flex gap-4 text-slate-400 leading-[1.5]"
                  >
                    Make room transitions easier
                  </li>
                  <li
                    class="start-at-05-list-li flex gap-4 text-slate-400 leading-[1.5]"
                  >
                    Build in short but meaningful breaks between sessions
                  </li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>
      </article>
    </main>

    <footer
      role="contentinfo"
      class="border-t border-slate-700 bg-slate-900 pt-8 pb-8 text-center text-xs font-normal text-slate-400"
    >
      <div class={containerClass}>
        <p>
          Start at <span class="text-orange-400">:05</span> — Smarter meeting times
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4">
          By <a
            href="https://www.garbereder.com"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="text-orange-400 hover:text-orange-600 focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-orange-500 rounded"
            >Gerrit Garbereder</a
          >
        </p>
      </div>
    </footer>
  </div>
</Main>
